snippet.title: Playing UNO Stacko challenge | Kids games to play | UNO Stacko game
snippet.description:
Kids love surprise and especially getting a new toy every day. But as parents, one should make their play time not only fun with good toys but also a learning medium for them. Children learn the most through toys and so they should be given things that will not only make them happy but teach them something new.
UNO stacko is a wonderful game that kids can play together. It has numbers with different colors which can help children in learning quickly. The kids are supposed to read out the instructions first and then start playing the game. They can stack up the numbers as per their wish and form designs that they like.
This wonderful game is great for younger children who have just started learning and guessing numbers. Kids of all age can play it with ease and enjoy some sibling’s time together. Reading out the instructions have helped the girls in getting a better understanding of what are they supposed to do and that too all by themselves.
UNO stacko is different from other games and is easy for the kids to play. Not only is it fun but provides a great opportunity for the children to get a stronger hold on the numbers. Stack up according to the colors or form number pyramids; this fantastic game is a great time killer for children. Remove a block one by one and see if your stack breaks down. Let the heart skip a beat with every block you remove.

#unostacko #uno #3kidstv

Test your child's memory with Kids Memory Game (3 - 6 years) which has been specially designed to entertain your children especially your little boys and girls. Kids Memory Game (3 - 6 years) is a matching game to develop memory skills and is designed for children and preschool boys and girls.
★ FEATURES:
Kids Memory Game (3 - 6 years) is a matching game to develop memory skills of children.
Playing this matching game with your kids will help them improve their recognition while having fun.
Kids Memory Game (3 - 6 years) features four game mode: "Fruit, Halloween, Sports and Foods"
Kids Memory Game (Toddlers) is a game for children of all ages, babies, preschoolers, school children and teens. Both, boys and girls will love to play this game at leisure.

STEP 1 - Initially you will see all cards turned face down. Tap on one of the card and remember the picture on it. With the next tap try to find and flip the card with the same picture as previous one.
STEP 2 - If the pictures on the both memory cards will be the same, they will stay opened and you can continue with the next pair. Otherwise both cards will flip back over and you will get another try. Try to find all matched cards as fast as possible.
